author: hustla187
title: classic paradisa
review: This is a mix of boys and girl's versions of Lego. The lighthouse looks very cool and the windsurfer and the BBQ grill look perfect the way the are. If I had to pick two Paradisa sets, this would actually be one of them. Definitely a 5 out of 5.

author: Elle82
title: Love it
review: This set comes with lots of little elements including a very clever bbq, and another set of those pink stairs we all love. I dont think its too girly at all, its a light house!! Love the baseboard also
